product_description.Immersive 17.32 cm (6.82) HD+ Display: Watch your favourite superheroes win epic battles on this smartphone's 17.32 cm (6.82) HD+ Drop notch display. Its narrow bezel and 20.5:9 aspect ratio enhance its luxurious appeal, enabling you to see more of your favourite content. While this smartphone's 1500:1 contrast ratio and 440 nits brightness ensure rich image quality, its 90.6% screen-to-body ratio makes it a delight to view your favourite content.
product_description.13 MP AI Dual Rear Camera: Capture the beautiful details of your city's nightlife with this smartphone's 13 MP AI Dual rear camera, which features a 13 MP primary lens, a low-light sensor, and a quad-LED flash. You can even capture stunning pictures even in dim-light conditions. To help you capture breathtaking landscape shots, this smartphone is also equipped with an Auto Scene detection function that can easily recognize up to nine outdoor settings. And, if you're looking forward to unleashing your inner filmmaker, you can make fair use of this smartphone's Slo-mo video recording feature, Bokeh mode, and AI HDR feature.
product_description.8 MP AI Selfie Camera with LED Flash: You can use this smartphone's 8 MP AI selfie camera of f/2.0 aperture and its convenient LED flash to click fascinating images, both in portrait and wide-selfie mode. This smartphone's 3D Face Beauty mode helps you spruce up your selfies with flawless skin, enlarged eyes, and a slim face.
product_description.Massive 6000 mAh Battery: This smartphone's 6000 mAh battery is backed by a Power Marathon technology that regulates the power consumption according to how you use your apps. With the combination of the robust battery and Power Marathon technology, this smartphone helps you enjoy almost 23 hours of video playback time, nearly 44 hours of music playback time, and about 53 hours of 4G talktime. Additionally, this smartphone also restricts the power consumed by the backstage-running mechanism of apps, thereby extending its battery life by up to 3 hours.
product_description.Responsive Helio G25 Octa-core Processor: Crafted for the active gamer, this smartphone features a 12 nm Helio G25 2.0 GHz octa-core processor, alongside 2 GB of RAM, to keep you engaged in multiple gameplays. Plus, if you have many cherished moments and tunes, you can benefit from this smartphone's inbuilt memory capacity of up to 32 GB. You don't need to worry about running out of space as you can get an additional 256 GB of memory with an external SD card (sold separately). This smartphone also comes with a dual 4G SIM slot to complement your calling requirements.
product_description.Head-turning Design: This smartphone wraps all its features in an elegant gem-cut texture design. Its back is beautified by a stunning flow pattern and the rectangular camera module lens. With a 2.5D glass finish back, narrow bezel panel, and 2.5D curved glass on the front, this smartphone is bound to fetch you compliments.
product_description.Cinematic Sound Quality: You can now catch the subtle nuances in iconic dialogues, thanks to this smartphone's DTS + HD Surround Sound feature. Moreover, this smartphone can easily adapt to all your audio entertainment needs with dedicated audio modes for gaming, videos, and music.
product_description.Dynamic Security Measures: This smartphone enables you to securely access it through a fingerprint sensor or the face unlock feature, giving you two options to choose from. The multipurpose fingerprint sensor also allows you to answer calls and dismiss morning alarms with a simple tap. You can also access different apps quickly by syncing the apps with different fingers.
product_description.XOS 7 Dolphin for Android: Equipped with the XOS 7 Dolphin OS, powered by Android 10 (Go edition), this smartphone comes with a host of impressive features. With this operating system, you can enjoy the benefits of Wi-Fi sharing, Smart Gestures, location controls, Digital Wellbeing, Dark Theme, Smart Panel, Game Mode, Clean In AI Gallery, Social Turbo, and more.
